summary: After watching Taylor Swift's AMAs opening performance yesterday made me wanting to watch her Reputation Stadium Tour in Tokyo...
body: After watching Taylor Swift’s AMAs opening performance yesterday made me wanting to watch her Reputation Stadium Tour in Tokyo more than ever since there is no Philippines in the tour schedule and it’ll be my first time then to watch her live. Too bad though, I can’t buy a ticket unless I’m in Japan or I have a Japan-issued card for online transactions. And the last time I checked, it is already sold-out. I can’t trust those online ticket resellers.

summary:
Dear Taylor 😊
You have been the bright guiding light in my darkness ✨
I just wanted to start by saying thank you 🙏🏻 I know a lot...
body:
We are all Gorgeous inside and out 💛✨🏳️‍🌈

Dear Taylor 😊


You have been the bright guiding light in my darkness ✨


I just wanted to start by saying thank you 🙏🏻 I know a lot of the fans have said that you have helped them through their darkest time. It’s true, you and your music have really helped me through my darkest time.


At first, accepting the person I am was really difficult. It took a very long time and a LOT of encouragement. I cried and I felt pain in my darkness. But you were there. You were the light that I followed. And I escaped my darkness.


I came out and it was the best thing I’ve done. It was the best feeling in the whole wide world. With you by my side, I’ve become a happier person and I LOVE the person I am. It is all because of you


I won’t forget hearing your beautiful song “Change” from Fearless. It is one of my favourite song. The song really reminds me of the fact that in the future, our world will change. The walls WILL fall down and everyone will be equal. There will be peace. And everyone will come together. That is the future I want for us all. 💛🏳️‍🌈💛


YOU’RE SO GORGEOUS AND I WILL SAY THAT TO YOUR FACE WHEN I MEET YOU ONE DAY 💛💛 a boy can dream 💛✨💝😊


On behalf of all your fans, Thank you for everything 💛 @taylorswift @taylornation


Lots of love ~ Pep
